-Awsat|accessdate=30 March 2017|date=11 March 2017|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321042628/http://english.aawsat.com/s-alabyad/news-middle-east/yemeni-officer-4-lebanese-hezbollah-members-caught-marib|archivedate=21 March 2017}}\n*{{cite web|last1=Pestano|first1=Andrew V.|title=Yemen accuses Hezbollah of supporting Houthi attacks in Saudi Arabia|url=http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2016/02/25/Yemen-accuses-Hezbollah-of-supporting-Houthi-attacks-in-Saudi-Arabia/4971456399472/|website=www.upi.com|publisher=United Press International|date=25 February 2016|location=Sana'a, Yemen|accessdate=30 March 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317143211/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/World-News/2016/02/25/Yemen-accuses-Hezbollah-of-supporting-Houthi-attacks-in-Saudi-Arabia/4971456399472/|archivedate=17 March 2017}}\n*{{cite web|last1=Hatem|first1=Mohammed|title=Yemen Accuses Hezbollah of Helping Houthis in Saudi Border War|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-02-24/yemen-accuses-hezbollah-of-helping-houthis-in-saudi-border-war|website=www.bloomberg.com|publisher=Bloomberg News|accessdate=30 March 2017|date=24 February 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331080303/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-02-24/yemen-accuses-hezbollah-of-helping-houthis-in-saudi-border-war|archivedate=31 March 2017}}\n*{{cite web|title=Yemen government says Hezbollah fighting alongside Houthis|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security-idUSKCN0VX21N|website=www.reuters.com|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=30 March 2017|date=24 February 2016|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317061812/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security-idUSKCN0VX21N|archivedate=17 March 2017}}\n*{{cite web|title=Report: Houthi Commander Admits Iran, Hezbollah Training Fighters in Yemen|url=http://www.thetower.org/4440-report-houthi-commander-admits-iran-hezbollah-training-fighters-in-yemen/|website=www.thetower.org|publisher=The Tower|accessdate=30 March 2017|date=17 January 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317054602/http://www.thetower.org/4440-report-houthi-commander-admits-iran-hezbollah-training-fighters-in-yemen/|archivedate=17 March 2017}}</ref>\n<!--  <ref name=\"Taiz rocket attack\">See:\n*{{cite web|title=December 2015 Taiz rocket attack|url=https://www.ibtimes.com/saudi-coalition-houthi-rebels-intensify-attacks-yemen-ahead-proposed-ceasefire-2223830|website=www.ibntimes.com|publisher=International Business Times}} </ref>-->\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{external media\n| align  = right\n| width  = 220px\n| video1 = {{YouTube|CwwP3SiBIC8|The US may be aiding war crimes in Yemen}}\n| video2 = {{YouTube|f9qwbLAyanY|PBS Report from Yemen: As Millions Face Starvation, American-Made Bombs Are Killing Civilians}}}}\n{{Commons category|Yemeni Civil War (2015)}}\n*[http://midwestdiplomacy.com/2015/01/26/demystifying-yemens-conflict/ Demystifying Yemen's Conflict (Midwest Diplomacy)]\n*[http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/pdf/10.1080/03068374.2015.1037162 Yemen and the Huthis: Genesis of the 2015 Crisis (Asian Affairs Journal)]\n*[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/country_profiles/1706450.stm Timeline: Yemen (BBC)]\n*[https://news.vice.com/article/as-saudis-block-a-human-rights-inquiry-in-yemen-the-us-stays-quiet As Saudis Block a Human Rights Inquiry in Yemen, America Stays Quiet]. ''[[Vice (magazine)|Vice]].'' 1 October 2015.\n*[https://www.hrw.org/news/2015/12/21/yemen-coalition-bombs-homes-capital Yemen: Coalition Bombs Homes in Capital]. [[Human Rights Watch]]. 21 December 2015.\n*[https://www.thenation.com/article/the-united-states-may-be-guilty-of-war-crimes-in-yemen/ The United States May Be Guilty of War Crimes in Yemen]. ''[[The Nation]].'' November 2016.\n*[http://www.tomdispatch.com/post/176220/tomgram%3A_rebecca_gordon%2C_yet_another_undeclared_u.s._war/ Tomgram: Rebecca Gordon, Yet Another Undeclar